        %h2
          Jared Spool
          .lineup.lineup-wrap
            .h-sm-caps-gray Founder, User Interface Engineering, &amp; Co-founder, Centre Center
        
        %p Jared M. Spool is the founder of User Interface Engineering, the largest usability research organization of its kind in the world. If you&#8217;ve ever seen Jared speak about usability, you know that he&#8217;s probably the most effective and knowledgeable communicator on the subject today.

